These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, montecristo, ritmeester, havana
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, balloon-flower, lily
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growslily and the fan of techno##2
10. the siglo-smoker is the person who growslily##1
11. the fan of funk is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | ritmeester  | siglo    | havana    | montecristo   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Hobby   | drawing | photography | reading    | magic-tricks |
| Flower           | zinnia | lily       | daisy | balloon-flower     |

