.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, jet-ski, ship
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, pink, orange, lavender
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, canasta, backgammon
 1. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
 2. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the person who likes grey##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 9. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the person who likes orange is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Transport         | jet-ski | ship | trike   | roller |
| Color   | orange | grey   | pink   | lavender    |
| Game         | canasta | backgammon  | chess | snooker   |

