.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, skydiving, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, animation, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, poppy, aconite
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 2. the egyptian is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is the italian##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the british##1
10. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby      | camping | skydiving   | woodworking    | baking      |
| Movie-Genre           | animation | thriller | zombie | time-travel     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Flower           | aconite         | zinnia       | poppy  | daffodil       |

