.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, bartender, software-developer, writer
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, rat, snake
House: ranch-style, victorian, art-deco, colonial
 1. the photographer is the person eating corn##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 4. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
 5. the bartender is the colonial house##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the left of the photographer##1
 7. the writer is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the art-deco house is the owner of the pony##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the software-developer is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | writer       | software-developer   | photographer   | bartender   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| Pet      | snake | pony    | rat  | chinchilla |
| House      | victorian  | art-deco  | ranch-style | colonial    |

