.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, snooker, go
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, indie, jazz, electronic
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, chinchilla, lizard
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing go##2
 3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the fan of indie is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of r&b##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of indie##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
10. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Game    | snooker    | go      | backgammon          | mah-jongg    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Music-Genre     | electronic     | jazz      | indie     | r&b |
| Pet   | rabbit   | lizard | chinchilla        | ferret   |

