The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, dahlia, begonia
 1. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsdahlia##2
 3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is between the person who likes black and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

