|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | soy-milk   | sprite     | water   |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | car       | bus | taxi |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster     | scientific   | thriller     | romance     |
| Food         | cranberry | cabbage | grapefruit   | mango |

