.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, bus, trike
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, indie, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: french, spanish, polish, turkish
 1. the spanish is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the turkish is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4
 5. the french is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the polish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Transport      | bus       | car | helicopter        | trike        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | reggae        | hip-hop    | indie      |
| Nationality         | spanish     | polish    | turkish | french   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, action, disaster, comedy
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, lavender, ivory, chestnut
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, dressmaker, scientist, entrepreneur
 1. the fan of techno is the person who likes ivory##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 6. the fan of house is the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the scientist is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 8. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
10. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | comedy  | action     | spy |
| Color         | lavender    | light-blue | ivory      | chestnut |
| Job     | entrepreneur | dressmaker     | scientist | analyst       |

 